00:04:50.280 --> 00:04:53.440
First of all, entertainment apps
should be highly visual.

00:04:53.570 --> 00:04:56.430
If you're designing for the iPhone,
really take advantage

00:04:56.430 --> 00:04:57.950
of the retina display.

00:04:58.050 --> 00:05:01.480
If you're designing for the iPad,
make sure you showcase the content

00:05:01.530 --> 00:05:03.460
on the large 10-inch screen.

00:05:03.620 --> 00:05:08.130
The layout, graphics, and typography,
they all need to look great.

00:05:08.300 --> 00:05:10.590
You're competing with thousands
of other apps on the app

00:05:10.590 --> 00:05:13.950
stores in several categories,
and a lot of people are gonna decide

00:05:13.980 --> 00:05:18.290
to download your app based purely
on how good your screenshots look.

00:05:18.590 --> 00:05:21.060
Entertainment apps should also be fun.

00:05:21.110 --> 00:05:24.550
Users typically spend a lot
more time in entertainment apps,

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:26.620
and the experience
shouldn't feel like a chore.

