00:06:03.670 --> 00:06:07.180
Because you're trying to entertain,
you can be a little bit more

00:06:07.180 --> 00:06:08.930
gratuitous with animation and sound.

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:12.150
Compared to utility apps,
navigating content can be a

00:06:12.150 --> 00:06:14.320
little bit more exploratory too.

00:06:14.320 --> 00:06:18.210
The path to accessing multimedia
doesn't always need to be so linear.

00:06:18.220 --> 00:06:21.180
This is the Biophilia app from Bjork.

